    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package for submission to the regulatory review process on the basis that the Monte Carlo UQ bounds remain below the clinical hemolysis threshold at the 95th percentile and the identified gaps are documented with a remediation plan. The VerificationActivity for the mesh independence study (mesh-independence-study-vad) was declared and executed, but the associated evidence artifacts have not yet been formally archived and linked via prov:wasGeneratedBy, representing an open action item that does not preclude initial submission. All other validation results are linked to their generating activities.",
